  "title": "Architectural Manager (HDB/Condo/Landed Projects)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Lead the architectural design team and oversee design development.</li><li>Ensure designs comply with regulatory requirements and client expectations.</li><li>Review design proposals and provide innovative solutions for complex projects.</li><li>Coordinate with consultants and project managers for smooth design integration.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Architecture with strong technical knowledge.</li><li>At least 4 years’ experience in <strong>HDB, Condo, and Landed developments.</strong></li><li>Strong project management and client coordination skills.</li><li>Proficient in <strong>AutoCAD, Revit,</strong> or equivalent.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
